          },
          "description": "<p>Technologies: NodeJS, NestJS, PostgreSQL, Prisma, Redis, CQRS, DDD</p><p></p><p>• 𝗘𝗻𝗴𝗶𝗻𝗲𝗲𝗿𝗲𝗱 𝘀𝗼𝗹𝘂𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻𝘀 𝘁𝗼 𝗼𝗽𝘁𝗶𝗺𝗶𝘇𝗲 𝗵𝗲𝗮𝘃𝘆 𝘄𝗼𝗿𝗸𝗹𝗼𝗮𝗱 𝗽𝗿𝗼𝗰𝗲𝘀𝘀𝗲𝘀 and enhance system responsiveness using 𝗕𝘂𝗹𝗹𝗠𝗤 for robust task queuing and management.</p><p>• 𝗟𝗲𝗱 𝘁𝗵𝗲 𝗲𝘃𝗮𝗹𝘂𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝗮𝗻𝗱 𝘀𝗲𝗹𝗲𝗰𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝗼𝗳 𝘁𝗵𝗲 𝗽𝗿𝗶𝗺𝗮𝗿𝘆 𝗮𝘂𝘁𝗵𝗲𝗻𝘁𝗶𝗰𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝗮𝗻𝗱 𝗮𝘂𝘁𝗵𝗼𝗿𝗶𝘇𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝘀𝘁𝗮𝗰𝗸, choosing 𝗯𝗲𝘁𝘁𝗲𝗿-𝗮𝘂𝘁𝗵 for its developer-friendly frontend library, simplified setup, and essential multi-tenant capabilities.</p><p>• 𝗜𝗺𝗽𝗹𝗲𝗺𝗲𝗻𝘁𝗲𝗱 𝗮 𝗳𝗹𝗲𝘅𝗶𝗯𝗹𝗲, 𝗱𝘆𝗻𝗮𝗺𝗶𝗰 𝗔𝘁𝘁𝗿𝗶𝗯𝘂𝘁𝗲-𝗕𝗮𝘀𝗲𝗱 𝗔𝗰𝗰𝗲𝘀𝘀 𝗖𝗼𝗻𝘁𝗿𝗼𝗹 (ABAC) system using the 𝗖𝗔𝗦𝗟 library, empowering Workspace Owners to autonomously create and manage granular permission levels for their members.</p><p>• Deployed public-facing services onto 𝗖𝗹𝗼𝘂𝗱𝗳𝗹𝗮𝗿𝗲 𝗪𝗼𝗿𝗸𝗲𝗿𝘀 to significantly optimize resource usage and improve content delivery network (CDN) efficiency.</p><p>• Established the core data infrastructure, selecting 𝗣𝗼𝘀𝘁𝗴𝗿𝗲𝗦𝗤𝗟 as the primary relational database and 𝗣𝗿𝗶𝘀𝗺𝗮 as the ORM, then architecting and optimizing the initial database schema for performance and scalability.</p>",
          "roles": []
        },
