          "description": "<p>Technologies: Linux, MongoDB, Rust (Programming Language), PostgreSQL, Redis, Prisma ORM, NestJS, React.js, Polaris, BullMQ (Producer/Consumer Queue) , Shopify Apps , Shopify Themes, Shopify Functions (Rust), Shopify Api/GraphQL</p><p></p><p>• 𝗔𝗿𝗰𝗵𝗶𝘁𝗲𝗰𝘁𝗲𝗱 𝗮 𝘀𝗰𝗮𝗹𝗮𝗯𝗹𝗲, 𝗰𝗹𝗲𝗮𝗻-𝗮𝗿𝗰𝗵𝗶𝘁𝗲𝗰𝘁𝘂𝗿𝗲 𝗡𝗲𝘀𝘁𝗝𝗦 𝗯𝗮𝗰𝗸𝗲𝗻𝗱 specifically optimized for seamless integration with the 𝗦𝗵𝗼𝗽𝗶𝗳𝘆 𝗔𝗣𝗜.</p><p>• 𝗘𝗻𝗴𝗶𝗻𝗲𝗲𝗿𝗲𝗱 𝗮 𝗿𝗼𝗯𝘂𝘀𝘁 𝗿𝗮𝘁𝗲-𝗹𝗶𝗺𝗶𝘁 𝗺𝗮𝗻𝗮𝗴𝗲𝗺𝗲𝗻𝘁 𝘀𝘆𝘀𝘁𝗲𝗺 using 𝗕𝘂𝗹𝗹𝗠𝗤 to process asynchronous Shopify API calls (REST and GraphQL) efficiently, ensuring consistent service uptime and performance.</p><p>• 𝗗𝗲𝘃𝗲𝗹𝗼𝗽𝗲𝗱 𝗵𝗶𝗴𝗵-𝗽𝗲𝗿𝗳𝗼𝗿𝗺𝗮𝗻𝗰𝗲 𝗰𝘂𝘀𝘁𝗼𝗺 𝗱𝗶𝘀𝗰𝗼𝘂𝗻𝘁 𝗹𝗼𝗴𝗶𝗰 using 𝗥𝘂𝘀𝘁 and 𝗦𝗵𝗼𝗽𝗶𝗳𝘆 𝗙𝘂𝗻𝗰𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻𝘀, calculating complex pricing formulas based on real-time product and customer attributes.</p><p>• 𝗦𝘁𝗿𝗲𝗮𝗺𝗹𝗶𝗻𝗲𝗱 𝗲𝗺𝗮𝗶𝗹 𝗰𝗼𝗺𝗺𝘂𝗻𝗶𝗰𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻𝘀 by implementing an optimized templating structure using 𝗛𝗮𝗻𝗱𝗹𝗲𝗯𝗮𝗿𝘀, enhancing content delivery efficiency.</p><p>• 𝗠𝗮𝗻𝗮𝗴𝗲𝗱 𝗰𝗼𝗻𝘁𝗮𝗶𝗻𝗲𝗿𝗶𝘇𝗲𝗱 𝗱𝗲𝗽𝗹𝗼𝘆𝗺𝗲𝗻𝘁 and complex service interconnections using 𝗗𝗼𝗸𝗸𝘂, significantly improving application resilience and deployment speed.</p>",
